| 3.3 - Docker execution | DockerExecutor with container management | ✅ |
| 7.1-7.3 - Cloud integration | CloudExecutor with multi-provider support | ✅ |

### Design Patterns Used

1. **Strategy Pattern**: Different executors for different execution types
2. **Template Method**: BaseExecutor provides common execution flow
3. **Factory Pattern**: Executor selection based on node execution type
4. **Observer Pattern**: Progress updates through TaskContext
5. **Command Pattern**: TaskRequest encapsulates execution parameters

